**Operator-local runbook — NOT committed to remote.**

Copy this file to `CLAUDE-internal.md` (sibling of `CLAUDE.md`) and populate the placeholder IDs from your CTO handoff. The actual populated file is listed in `.gitignore` and must never be pushed.

Classification: **Internal**. Contains Airtable IDs, PMO protocol, and trust-boundary configuration.

