## Git workflow (operator notes)

- Always create a `feature/*` branch. Never commit directly to `main`.
- Open a PR for review.
- All pre-commit hooks must pass before pushing.
- Include the PR number in the Work Item's `## Execution Log`.
- For Dependabot PRs, see the current dependency policy in `.github/dependabot.yml` — some major-version ignores are in place (e.g. `@astrojs/svelte` pending coordinated Astro v6 upgrade WI).

